lead_paragraph: Manchester United winger Memphis Depay is keen to breathe fresh life into his faltering career in England under new manager Jose Mourinho after enduring a disappointing debut campaign under former boss Louis van Gaal.

headline.print_headline: Man Utd's Memphis Vows to Return Stronger Next Season
